- All elements in the diagonals of the integer 2D array parameter `grid` must be non-zero.
- All other elements in the integer 2D array parameter `grid` must be equal to 0.
- The boolean result is equal to the true literal if the integer 2D array parameter `grid` is an X-Matrix.
- The boolean result is equal to the false literal if the integer 2D array parameter `grid` is not an X-Matrix.